  <brief_title>Effect of Bifidobacterium Lactis HN019 on Colonic Transit Time and Digestive Symptoms</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Three‐Arm, Placebo Controlled, Double‐Blind, Single Center Study to Evaluate the Impact of Probiotic Strain Bifidobacterium Lactis HN019 on Intestinal Well‐Being, Colonic Transit Time and Digestive Discomfort</official_title>
